## üå∏ About Flores Victoria

Flores Victoria is an **open source enterprise-grade e-commerce platform** specifically designed for florists and flower shops. 

This project aims to provide the **most advanced and complete floristry e-commerce solution** available to the open source community, featuring:

- ü§ñ **AI-powered recommendations** with TensorFlow.js
- üí≥ **Multi-payment gateway** support (Stripe, PayPal, Transbank)
- üõ°Ô∏è **Enterprise security** with OWASP compliance
- üìä **Advanced monitoring** with Grafana/Prometheus
- ‚ò∏Ô∏è **Kubernetes-ready** microservices architecture
- üì± **Progressive Web App** with offline capabilities
- üåç **Multi-language & multi-currency** support

## üéØ Mission

Our mission is to democratize access to enterprise-level e-commerce technology for florists worldwide, enabling small and medium flower shops to compete with large corporations through cutting-edge technology.

## ü§ù Contributing

We welcome contributions from developers, designers, florists, and anyone passionate about open source technology and flowers! 

See [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md) for details on how to get started.

